highlights.text: TimelessRemixes has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Nhật ký tình đầu - Blues Rock” is the highest at #6.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 238 days straight.
“24h truoc khi anh 44” by Youngboidaikher is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #10.
“WYN?” by HAECHAN and HAON is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 23 spots at #74.
